cs.MM, cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.LG

This paper deals with multi-modal video classification using visual, audio, and text features. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.MM (Multimedia). The paper also involves natural language processing techniques for text classification, which suggests that it could belong to cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the paper uses computer vision techniques for video classification, which could place it in cs.CV (Computer Vision). The paper also involves machine learning techniques for classification, which could place it in cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper involves information retrieval techniques for text classification, which could place it in cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
